
# **JAWABAN POST-TEST PRAKTIKUM MONGODB**

## **1. Set-up cluster di MongoDB Atlas**

1. Buka [https://www.mongodb.com/cloud/atlas](https://www.mongodb.com/cloud/atlas)
2. Login / Sign Up akun MongoDB
3. Pilih menu **Cluster ‚Üí Build a Cluster**
4. Pilih **Free Tier (M0)**
5. Tentukan **Cluster Name, Provider, dan Region**
6. Klik **Create Deployment**
7. Cluster berhasil dibuat dan status **Running**

## **2. Membuat koneksi baru di MongoDB Compass**

1. Klik **Connect ‚Üí Choose connection method**
2. Pilih **MongoDB Compass**
3. Salin **connection string**
4. Buka aplikasi **MongoDB Compass**
5. Paste connection string
6. Klik **Save & Connect**
7. Koneksi berhasil terhubung

## **3. Membuat database dan collection**

1. Klik ikon **‚Äú+‚Äù (Create Database)**
2. Isi:

   * Database Name: `movieDB`
   * Collection Name: `users`
3. Klik **Create Database**
4. Tambahkan collection baru:

   * `movies`
   * `posts`

## **4. Insert document ke collection users**

```js
db.users.insertOne({
  username: "GoodGuyGreg",
  firstname: "Good Guy",
  lastname: "Greg"
})
```

‚úî Document berhasil ditambahkan

---

## **5. Insert banyak document (insertMany)**

```js
db.users.insertMany([
  {
    username: "GoodGuyGreg",
    firstname: "Good Guy",
    lastname: "Greg"
  },
  {
    username: "JohnDoe1234",
    firstname: "John",
    lastname: "Doe",
    yearjoined: 2005
  },
  {
    username: "SamJohnSings",
    firstname: "Sam John",
    lastname: "Sings",
    rating: 4.9
  }
])
```

‚úî Beberapa document berhasil ditambahkan

---

## **6. Import document ke collection movies**

1. Buka collection **movies**
2. Klik **Add Data ‚Üí Import File**
3. Pilih file **movies.json**
4. Klik **Import**
5. Import selesai dan data tampil di collection

---

## **7. Insert document ke collection posts**

1. Buka collection **posts**
2. Klik **Add Data ‚Üí Insert Document**
3. Paste isi file **posts.json**
4. Klik **Insert**
   ‚úî Document berhasil ditambahkan

---

## **8. Membuat query (find)**

a. Menampilkan semua data:

```js
db.movies.find()
```

b. Film oleh Quentin Tarantino:

```js
db.movies.find({ writer: "Quentin Tarantino" })
```

c. Film yang dimainkan Brad Pitt:

```js
db.movies.find({ actors: "Brad Pitt" })
```

d. Film tahun 90-an:

```js
db.movies.find({ year: { $gte: 1990, $lt: 2000 } })
```

e. Film yang memiliki sinopsis:

```js
db.movies.find({ synopsis: { $exists: true } })
```

---

## **9. Update document**

Menambahkan sinopsis pada film *The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey*:

```js
db.movies.updateOne(
  { title: "The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey" },
  {
    $set: {
      synopsis: "A reluctant hobbit, Bilbo Baggins, sets out on a journey with dwarves to reclaim their mountain home."
    }
  }
)
```

‚úî Data berhasil di-update

---

## **10. Delete document**

Menghapus film *Pulp Fiction*:

```js
db.movies.deleteOne({ title: "Pulp Fiction" })
```

Menghapus film Brad Pitt tahun 2000-an:

```js
db.movies.deleteMany({
  $and: [
    { actors: "Brad Pitt" },
    { year: { $gte: 2000 } }
  ]
})
```

‚úî Document berhasil dihapus


